{{Dynamic list}} {{Labor |expanded=Strikes}}
The following is a list of specific [[strike action|strikes]] (workers refusing to work in an attempt to change their conditions in a particular industry or an individual workplace, or in solidarity with those in another particular workplace) and [[general strike]]s (widespread refusal of workers to work in an organized political campaign on a broader national or international level). ==Chronological list of [[strike action|strikes]]==
