iners' strike (1969)|Unofficial strike by mineworkers over pay of surface workers]] (1969, UK)<ref>{{cite book |last=Douglas |first=David John |title=Pit Sense versus the State: A history of militant miners in the Doncaster area |location=London |publisher=Phoenic Press |pages=11–12 |isbn=0-948984-26-0 }}</ref>
